<P ALIGN=CENTER><B>Education:</B></P>
<P>I was born on the 16th of August 1968 in Palmanova (UD), Italy. <BR>I
have an univerisity degree in Physics, and finished my thesis
(&quot;<I>Numerical simulations of the origin of the structures in
the large scale universe</I>&quot;) on february 1994, at Padua
University (PD). <BR>In november 1996 I began a contract with the
&quot;Centro Servizi Agrometeorologici per il Friuli Venezia Giulia&quot;
(CSA), as researcher of the &quot;Thunderstorm and Hail Prevention
and Research Center&quot;, under the scientific direction of dr.
<A HREF="http://151.8.71.18/~www/IT/COMPRENSIONE/morgan/morgan.html">Griffith
Morgan</A>, and started my study in Meteorology. On first July 2000
CSA becomed the &quot;Osservatorio Meteorologico Regionale&quot;
dell'ARPA Friuli Venezia Giulia (<A HREF="http://www.osmer.fvg.it/">OSMER-ARPA</A>).
<BR>&nbsp; <BR>&nbsp; 
</P>
